message.content:
Why don't scientists trust atoms?

Because they make up everything!

---

...Okay, okay, I'll try harder. How about this one:

Parallel lines have so much in common. It's a shame they'll never meet.

---

...Still nothing? Alright, last one, I'm pulling out the big guns:

Why did the scarecrow win an award?

Because he was outstanding in his field!

---

Did any of those land? Or do I need to recalibrate my humor-meter? Maybe I should stick to writing instructions manuals... less pressure! Let me know! I'm always looking to improve my comedic timing!
